{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"ebf99dae39","title":"给文运昌“的信","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"fafec1d381","index":0,"year":1922,"month":11,"day":11,"articleId":"ebf99dae39"}],"tags":[{"id":"2a70b5d939","name":"书信","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji2","name":"毛泽东全集第2卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji2.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji2":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"5edd96f187","type":"paragraph","text":"给文运昌“的信","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji2","articleId":"ebf99dae39"},{"id":"22cf547b1d","type":"paragraph","text":"（1922年11月11日）运昌烟兄：来示接读。刘君实在无法位置，今刘回乡，情形请面询之。第在此无善足录，生活奇容，不足为戚友道也。男父母一函请面星。各位表兄嫂同此问候。有暇盼兄时赐教言。即颂乡祺！","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji2","articleId":"ebf99dae39"},{"id":"e9c5cf0de3","type":"paragraph","text":"弟泽东上","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji2","articleId":"ebf99dae39"},{"id":"7924a387ae","type":"paragraph","text":"十一月十一号[I]文远昌，字味昌，湖南都山市大坪乡大坪村磨家托（当时属乡）人，毛泽东的表兄。早年毕业于湖乡县立师范，在乡任小学教师。大革命时期曹参加农民运动，任酒多县风音多农民协会秘书等。新中国或立后，任湖","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji2","articleId":"ebf99dae39"}],"page":{"id":"e319e3f039","publicationId":"maoquanji2","articleId":"ebf99dae39","start":515,"end":515}}}},"__N_SSG":true}